snippet.title: Just Get Through Gameplay - Classic Run Level 30+ [Version 1.1.5] [HQ]
snippet.description:
You can see here a full Just Get Through Run to Level 30 in 1080p@60fps in Just Get Through Version 1.1.5 (Very outdated, check jusgetthrough.retrific.net for more up-to-date footage)
At the end there were still lives and TNT left but the video was already long enough. This video is here to show you that the game can get pretty easy once you get the feeling for the gameplay and also to show you how the game is like in the first levels. Just Get Through is a pretty difficult platformer, but everything is possible. You just need to know what you have to do. That's why you shouldn't give up. It's just a matter of time and will. 

Enjoy the gameplay. Uncensored and without any cuts in full resolution and max fps. Played with keyboard + mouse in Just Get Through Version 1.1.5

Get the game here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/338190
